title: The T-fal Optigrill +
description:
T-fal Optigrill + offers perfect grilling results from rare to well-done - at the touch of a button.  

The Optigrill features 6 cooking programs: Burgers, Poultry, Sandwiches, Sausage, Red Meat, Fish.  The Cooking indicator light changes from yellow to red and an audible beeps alert you when food is at rare, medium and well-done.  

The Frozen food function first defrosts and then cooks all types of food.
Use the Manual function for cooking vegetables or personal recipes.  A temperature gauge allows you to cook at high, medium or low.  


Drip-tray and plates are removable and dishwasher safe for easy clean-up.
